= reekmetric

Script to do some smell analyisis using reek on Rails applications.
For more information about reek http://wiki.github.com/kevinrutherford/reek

== Installation
Before you use it, you must install reek

sudo gem install reek

== Usage
Just put it on your RAILS_ROOT folder and run it

./reekmetric.sh

If you want a detailed reek output just run

./reekmetric.sh detailed

